com.philips.pins.shinelib

Interface SHNCapability

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    SHNCapabilityBattery, SHNCapabilityDataStreaming, SHNCapabilityDeviceDiagnostics, SHNCapabilityDeviceInformation, SHNCapabilityFirmwareUpdate, SHNCapabilityLogSynchronization, SHNCapabilityUserConfiguration
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CapabilityFirmwareUpdateDiComm, SHNCapabilityBatteryImpl, SHNCapabilityDeviceInformationCached, SHNCapabilityDeviceInformationImpl

    public interface SHNCapability
    A placeholder interface. Provides better type safety over using Object. SHNCapability is reported to the user of API via SHNDevice.getCapabilityForType(SHNCapabilityType). Returned instance is not type strong. The API user needs to cast it to the proper class type.
